[normal] more innovative
[normal] in design
[normal],
[normal] better reflecting the needs of
[normal] modern society
[normal] a
[normal]nd 
[normal]the small employer
[normal], enabling them to manage an appropriate qualification for the role the new entrant worker or apprentice would fulfill.  
